title: Did star guardian quiz..no icon?
body: So I did the quiz last night yet I still got no icon? Are they being delivered and its taking time or..?

replies.body: It does say it can take upto a week to get the icon when you do the quiz

I did mine last week as well and nothing
Ive been lied to

I got my icon 2~ days after I did the quiz, so it's most likely just taking a little to credit all the accounts that completed the quiz. If you haven't got it in a couple weeks, then I'd consider submitting a ticket, but for now, waiting is your best bet.
Same I did it last week still no Icon...inb4 scam
